The paper discusses network clustering and community detection, which are topics related to social networks and graph theory. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Other possible sub-categories include cs.SD (Software Engineering), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
